    <published>2023-03-08T07:35:05.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-03-08T09:11:21.296Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Typora学习"><a href="#Typora学习" class="headerlink" title="Typora学习"></a>Typora学习</h1><hr><h2 id="一、标题"><a href="#一、标题" class="headerlink" title="一、标题"></a>一、标题</h2><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308112229992.png" alt="image-20230308112229992" style="zoom:50%;" /><p><img src="/study-Typora/image-20230308111639805.png" alt="image-20230308111639805"></p><h2 id="二、段落"><a href="#二、段落" class="headerlink" title="二、段落"></a>二、段落</h2><h4 id="1、上下标"><a href="#1、上下标" class="headerlink" title="1、上下标"></a>1、上下标</h4><p>代码：</p><p>​<code>x^2^</code>       x^2^</p><p><code>H~2~o</code>    H<del>2</del></p><p><code>hello</code></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2、链接"><a href="#2、链接" class="headerlink" title="2、链接"></a>2、链接</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308111639805.png" alt="image-20230308111639805"></p><h4 id="2、分割线"><a href="#2、分割线" class="headerlink" title="2、分割线"></a>2、分割线</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308111832933.png" alt="image-20230308111832933"></p><h2 id="三、文字显示"><a href="#三、文字显示" class="headerlink" title="三、文字显示"></a>三、文字显示</h2><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308142933645.png" alt="image-20230308142933645"></p><p>如何打出‘*’    ：*1*2*3</p><h2 id="四、列表"><a href="#四、列表" class="headerlink" title="四、列表"></a>四、列表</h2><h4 id="1、无序列表"><a href="#1、无序列表" class="headerlink" title="1、无序列表"></a>1、无序列表</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308143551987.png" alt="image-20230308143551987"></p><p>-<br>    - ​<br>        - ​</p><h4 id="2、有序列表"><a href="#2、有序列表" class="headerlink" title="2、有序列表"></a>2、有序列表</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308144522278.png" alt="image-20230308144522278"></p><h4 id="3、任务列表"><a href="#3、任务列表" class="headerlink" title="3、任务列表"></a>3、任务列表</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308145243561.png" alt="image-20230308145243561"></p><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 学Typora</li></ul><h2 id="五、区块显示"><a href="#五、区块显示" class="headerlink" title="五、区块显示"></a>五、区块显示</h2><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308145726855.png" alt="image-20230308145726855"></p><blockquote><p>​第一层</p><blockquote><p>​第二层</p><blockquote><p>第三层</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><h2 id="六、代码显示"><a href="#六、代码显示" class="headerlink" title="六、代码显示"></a>六、代码显示</h2><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308150004628.png" alt="image-20230308150004628"></p><h2 id="七、链接"><a href="#七、链接" class="headerlink" title="七、链接"></a>七、链接</h2><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308150059244.png" alt="image-20230308150059244"></p><h2 id="八、脚注"><a href="#八、脚注" class="headerlink" title="八、脚注"></a>八、脚注</h2><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308150159344.png" alt="image-20230308150159344"></p><p>这是一个技术活<a href="%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%3Cbr%3E%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E8%A1%8C%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E">^1</a>（若是说明较长，可使用</br>进行换行：不包括‘&#x2F;’</p><h2 id="九、图片插入"><a href="#九、图片插入" class="headerlink" title="九、图片插入"></a>九、图片插入</h2><p><img src="C:\Users\zam\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230308151130223.png" alt="image-20230308151130223"></p><h2 id="十、插入表格"><a href="#十、插入表格" class="headerlink" title="十、插入表格"></a>十、插入表格</h2><p>快捷键：CTRL+T</p><h2 id="十一、数学公式的插入"><a href="#十一、数学公式的插入" class="headerlink" title="十一、数学公式的插入"></a>十一、数学公式的插入</h2>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
